<p><strong>Deployments</strong>: it includes changes in scripts</p>
<p><strong>Production Environment:</strong> NetSuite Production - all count=
ries / instances</p>
<p><strong>Hotfix</strong>: correction that needs to be released as quickly=
 as possible</p>
<p><strong>Release Management:</strong> Change Management</p>
